      "content": "wait so you're saying it is okay to take them together as long as I space them out? i was just thinking if i took them at the same time it might just hit faster. if i take the melatonin now and then the ambien in 20 mins, is there really that much of a risk? i'm just looking for a definitive yes or no so i can finally get some rest.",
